General.Name: Svetofor Group PAO
General.Description: JSC Svetofor Group provides educational services for training drivers on various vehicle. The company was formerly known as OOO PDD.TV and changed its name to JSC Svetofor Group in 2017. JSC Svetofor Group was incorporated in 2010 and is based in Saint Petersburg, Russia.
